reviewText:
i would give it one star because its not what i expected. don't fall for the cover of the case its a rip off its horrible
do not buy it its not what you think. it may look like the three stooges scrapbook but its the new three stooges and the inside was broken and the disk was loose and it was not a good perchase. but what ever you do do not fall for the cover on the case

greg macholl
